QuestData.Title: Blood Elf Plans
QuestData.Description: These plans seem important. You should take them to Vindicator Aldar at the crash site.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Blood Elf Plans to Vindicator Aldar at the Crash Site in Ammen Vale.
QuestData.RewardText: Here, let me read those plans.$B$BThe blood elves have followed us here? They are evil to the core and should be wiped from existence!$B$B<The vindicator takes a moment to regain his composure.>$B$BI apologize, that was uncalled for. We are indebted to you for uncovering this information, $n.
